                    Scale 1 cm represents <m>5^\circ C</m>
                </p>
                <image>
                    <latex-image>
                        \begin{tikzpicture}
                            \begin{axis}[
                               xlabel={Month},
                               ylabel={Average Temperature in ℃ },
                               xtick=data,
                               xticklabels={Mon, Tue, Wed, Thur, Fri, Sat, Sun},
                               ymin=0, ymax=60,
